### Install Next.js Auth Helpers Library using npm

Source: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/docs/content/guides/auth/auth-helpers/nextjs.mdx

Installs the Supabase Auth helpers package for Next.js along with the core Supabase JavaScript client library. These packages enable authentication functionality across Next.js App Router components and server-side contexts. Note that this package is deprecated and migration to @supabase/ssr is recommended.

```sh
